一位抗疫护士的三重身份：我不怕死，只是怕和孩子分开 | 口述实录。
The triple identity of an anti-epidemic nurse: I'm not afraid of death, but I'm afraid to tell a story separately from my child.
北青深一度。
North Qingsheng one degree.
